OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather wet start with a band
OL,6,Fof rain breaking up into a mix of
OL,7,Fbright spells and showers. Showers
OL,8,Fperhaps easing a little this afternoon
OL,9,Fahead of a band of rain reaching the
OL,10,Ffar southwest later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome late spells of sunshine
OL,13,Fin the east this evening. Otherwise
OL,14,Frain will spread across the region
OL,15,Fovernight, accompanied by blustery
OL,16,Fwinds. A milder night than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
