OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAny lingering rain in the
OL,6,Feast quickly clearing, leaving a
OL,7,Fblustery day with a mix of sunshine
OL,8,Fand showers. The showers will be heavy
OL,9,Fand possibly thundery, before easing
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FFurther showers likely on Wednesday,
OL,14,Fbefore turning drier, brighter and
OL,15,Fwarmer on Thursday. Mostly sunny and
OL,16,Fvery warm on Friday with perhaps the
OL,17,Fodd shower developing later in the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
